OL,3,CRecord installations of solar panels,
OL,4,Cbatteries and heat pumps so far in 2025
OL,6,FA record number of solar panels,
OL,7,Fbatteries and heat pumps have been
OL,8,Finstalled in UK homes and buildings in
OL,9,Fthe first six months of 2025, figures
OL,10,Fshow.
OL,12,FData from MCS (Microgeneration
OL,13,FCertification Scheme), the quality
OL,14,Fmark for small-scale renewables, found
OL,15,Fthere were more than 172,000 certified
OL,16,Finstallations between January and June
OL,17,Fthis year.
