OL,3,CRecord installations of solar panels,
OL,4,Cbatteries and heat pumps so far in 2025
OL,6,FThat is up 37% from the same period in
OL,7,F2024 and a third above the previous
OL,8,Frecord high start to the year, in
OL,9,F2023, the figures show.
OL,11,FThe MCS said the jump in installations
OL,12,Fwas being driven by three
OL,13,Ftechnologies: solar panels, electric
OL,14,Fheat pumps and battery storage.
OL,16,FThe top technology is solar panels,
OL,17,Fwith 123,000 certified installations
OL,18,Fin the first six months of 2025 ` a
OL,19,Frecord that breaks the previous
OL,20,FJanuary-to-June high set in 2012.
