OL,3,CRecord installations of solar panels,
OL,4,Cbatteries and heat pumps so far in 2025
OL,6,FThere were more than 18,000
OL,7,Finstallations of batteries, which can
OL,8,Fallow households to capture excess
OL,9,Fpower from solar panels or charge up
OL,10,Ffrom the grid when electricity is
OL,11,Fcheap and then use it at more
OL,12,Fexpensive peak times to cut bills.
OL,14,FThe figure is more than double the
OL,15,Fnear 8,000 batteries installed in the
OL,16,Fsame period in 2024, the MCS said.
