OL,3,CRecord installations of solar panels,
OL,4,Cbatteries and heat pumps so far in 2025
OL,6,FMeanwhile, certified installations of
OL,7,Fhighly efficient heat pumps, which run
OL,8,Fon electricity to draw heat from the
OL,9,Fair or ground to warm homes and heat
OL,10,Fwater, reached 30,000 in the first
OL,11,Fhalf of the year, up 12% on the first
OL,12,Fhalf of 2024.
OL,14,FThe figures also show that there were
OL,15,Falmost 50,000 renewable installations
OL,16,Fon newbuild properties, accounting for
OL,17,F28% of the total for the year so far,
OL,18,Fand significantly up on the first half
OL,19,Fof 2024, when they made up 21% of the
OL,20,F125,000 installations overall.
