OL,4,Cbatteries and heat pumps so far in 2025
OL,6,FThe MCS said that, with the Future
OL,7,FHomes Standard set to mandate solar
OL,8,Fpanels and low carbon heating in
OL,9,Fnewbuild homes from 2027, there was
OL,10,Fmassive potential for growth in the
OL,11,Flow carbon tech industry as the
OL,12,FGovernment attempts to boost house
OL,13,Fbuilding.
OL,15,FAnd the organisation said one of the
OL,16,Fkey drivers behind the increasing
OL,17,Fnumber of renewable installations was
OL,18,Fgovernment financial support, through
OL,19,Fschemes such as the #7,500 grant for
OL,20,Fnew heat pumps to replace boilers in
OL,21,Fhomes.
