OL,6,FThe latest available figures from
OL,7,FJanuary to March show that about three
OL,8,Fquarters of heat pump installations
OL,9,Fwere wholly or partially supported
OL,10,Fwith government funding.
OL,12,FIan Rippin, chief executive at MCS,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Across all renewable
OL,14,Ftechnologies, we are seeing a dramatic
OL,15,Frise in the number of installations
OL,16,Fbeing delivered into homes, helping to
OL,17,Freduce energy bills for consumers and
OL,18,Fdrive down emissions.
